{"tid":1077772,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"再一直自怨自艾，就等住被淘汰","createTime":"2019-03-25T22:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T10:13:17.000Z","uid":101558,"like":50,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e819e5d82739aa196c22539c985d1acc10371853","tid":1077772,"uid":101558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T22:53:00.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n朋友最近返左中國講書<br />\n係同啲在職既人上一個月堂咁<br />\n佢既感想係大陸人好勁<br />\n三個鐘既課程內容<br />\n佢地可以係落堂一個鐘之後就有人可以打哂個講者講過咩<br />\n係連語氣都有埋<br />\n堂上面介紹三本幾百頁既英文書<br />\n半班人會真係三星期內睇哂<br />\n重會sd email問啲有質素既問題<br />\n當中顯示到佢地有認真睇本書<br />\n<br />\n呢班就係落黎香港搵食既對手<br />\n佢地要既人工係一萬就得<br />\n如果香港人再繼續懶懶閒<br />\n覺得自己天之驕子，唔洗努力既<br />\n就祝你地好運<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ca8c9746065f844966688e6415a3acc920a4e1","tid":1077772,"uid":101558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T23:18:42.000Z","msg":"重成日等政府打救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1073ee949f883c73c724530a9f8f32e9399b312","tid":1077772,"uid":40470,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T23:23:19.000Z","msg":"香港勝在有IVE<br />\n<br />\nIVE仔世界第一<br />\n<br />\nIVE FG人工50k(自稱)"},{"pid":"a637979a7a9e7f39c748c9387adef61ac0c19fae","tid":1077772,"uid":101558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e1073ee949f883c73c724530a9f8f32e9399b312","tid":1077772,"uid":40470,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T23:23:19.000Z","msg":"香港勝在有IVE<br />\n<br />\nIVE仔世界第一<br />\n<br />\nIVE FG人工50k(自稱)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T23:39:58.000Z","msg":"係既話就唔會個個買唔到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05ac4d6d3406fe8d3d85528dc0237f92